snippet.title: 9 R.I.P. Official Trailer
snippet.description:
9 R.I.P. is a horror romance otome game developed by Otomate. Get swept away as Japanese urban legends, ghosts, demons, and spirits all come to life in this unique tale of horror and romance. 

Game Page: https://blerdyotome.com/games/9-r-i-p/
